originalText.text: dr. cho is a wonderful dentist.  i had avoided going to the dentist for years after a previous bad experience with someone else, but now i make sure to see dr. cho at least twice a year.  he has done a lot of work for me including replacing old fillings, a crown, and removing my wisdom teeth.  all work was done very well and he uses the latest materials and technology.  he is also kind and not judgmental, which is so appreciated.  i highly recommend dr. cho for all your dental needs.

originalText.text: Dr. Cho is the best. He isn't a "Drill Happy" dentist. He is as considerate and professional as his wonderful team. I've recommended so many friends to his practice and all are happy with his high standard of expert care. Love the classical music in the lobby!

originalText.text: Dr Cho is great as always. But my review is for his horrible  receptionist/ assistant ? after they moved to this new location.  she has an an attitude problem and should not be in the servicing industrial. I understand everyone is human and has bad days too but do not take it out on a customer. be professorial and talk pleasantly to your customer. I never had issues like this with his prior receptionist (a nice well manner young man) I had a very unpleasant ending experience which has never happened before in the many years that I been a patient. this is unacceptable as a customer. I will inform Dr Cho of this in the next visit as I feel this reflect badly on his otherwise great service.
